  "prompt": "What is the average and highest package of Galgotia University Noida?",
  "response": "As of my last knowledge update in October 2023, the average and highest salary packages at Galgotias University, Noida, can vary by year and by program. Generally, the average package for graduates from engineering programs tends to be around INR 4 to 6 lakhs per annum, while the highest packages can sometimes reach up to INR 15 to 25 lakhs per annum, depending on industry demand, student performance, and placement efforts.\n\nFor the most accurate and current information regarding placement statistics, I recommend checking the official Galgotias University website or contacting their placement cell directly, as these figures can change annually based on various factors.",
